## HTTP User-Agent propagation — all API calls now tagged as OntoBricks

### Context
Only the industry ontology importers (FIBO, IOF, FHIR, CDISC) were sending
`User-Agent: OntoBricks/<version>`. All internal Databricks REST calls,
loopback agent calls, LLM calls, and MCP server calls were missing the tag,
making it impossible to identify OntoBricks traffic in server logs.

### Changes
1. `src/back/core/databricks/DatabricksAuth.py` — added `"User-Agent": HTTP_USER_AGENT` to both branches of `get_auth_headers()` (PAT + OAuth) and to the OIDC token request; covers all downstream services that call this method (UnityCatalog, DashboardService, SQLWarehouse, WorkspaceService, SQLWizardService).
2. `src/back/core/databricks/VolumeFileService.py` — added UA to `_headers()` return dict.
3. `src/back/core/graphdb/lakebase/SyncedTableManager.py` — added UA to inline headers dict in `_call_api`.
4. `src/back/objects/mapping/Mapping.py` — added UA to inline headers dict; added `HTTP_USER_AGENT` to constants import.
5. `src/shared/fastapi/health.py` — added UA to Accelerated Sync probe headers; added `HTTP_USER_AGENT` to constants import.
6. `src/agents/tools/documents.py` — added UA to `_headers()` return dict.
7. `src/agents/llm_utils.py` — merge UA into a local copy of `headers` before each POST (avoids mutating the caller's dict).
8. `src/agents/agent_dtwin_chat/tools.py` — added UA as base header in `httpx.Client` factory.
9. `src/agents/agent_cohort/tools.py` — same.
10. `src/mcp-server/server/app.py` — added `_USER_AGENT = "OntoBricks-MCP/1.0.0"` constant; applied to `_client()` factory (`httpx.AsyncClient`) and the OAuth token request (`httpx.Client`).
11. `tests/units/auth/test_auth.py` — updated three `get_auth_headers` assertions to expect the new `User-Agent` key; import `HTTP_USER_AGENT` instead of hardcoding.

### Modified files
- `src/back/core/databricks/DatabricksAuth.py`
- `src/back/core/databricks/VolumeFileService.py`
- `src/back/core/graphdb/lakebase/SyncedTableManager.py`
- `src/back/objects/mapping/Mapping.py`
- `src/shared/fastapi/health.py`
- `src/agents/tools/documents.py`
- `src/agents/llm_utils.py`
- `src/agents/agent_dtwin_chat/tools.py`
- `src/agents/agent_cohort/tools.py`
- `src/mcp-server/server/app.py`
- `tests/units/auth/test_auth.py`

### Test result
422 passed, 1 skipped (units) — all tests green after updating assertions.

